Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「薔薇少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？紀  今天也不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  因為純的情況不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  紀也真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎車回家要小心哦  因為你總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也空空的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  宅配送東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩蓋個章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩蓋個章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩蓋個章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩蓋個章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩蓋個章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…  純
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻田先生  宅配送東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核對下面的項目之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放進桌子的第二個抽屜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工精靈「荷裡耶」會從異次元前來回收
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妖精還有異次元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是難得一見  令人驚奇的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,500)}要轉嗎    還是不轉\N\N{\fs22}恭喜您  櫻田先生！！！\N您是從9767251人中嚴格抽選出來的日本幸運兒！！！\N！！！無需涉及任何費用！！！\N即可得到幸運人偶禮品！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…純
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了  進來之前要先敲門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  今天也寄來了好多包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有幸福金銀珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個透視眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些全都是我郵購來的  不要隨便打開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…不要再做這種事了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要什麼東西的話  姐姐買給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我唯一的嗜好了  不想被別人干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是別人  是你姐姐啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很煩耶  你這個洗衣膠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(「膠」音同「紀」)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是這種怪怪的郵購  也有很多是詐騙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些時候電視也播過…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄到家裡  讓我笑過一遍之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在試用期之內退還  就不用付錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會買到很珍貴的寶物  這種冒險刺激的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無法忍受的誘惑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…純
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在心裡在想我很陰暗對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我很狡詐對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得你可能會遭到一點報應…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:07:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其玩這個  不如去找些譬如打棍球之類的開朗興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  感覺不錯  純說不定會很有天分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在客廳的東西  今天不寄回去的話就不能退錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  純…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少再跟姐姐一起吃飯好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐想聽聽你現在的興趣  想開心的跟你聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  你一定又可以去學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去退貨啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會來不及的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好心情都被你毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…我的腳趾甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡怎麼有這種東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是人偶吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好大…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好逼真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微玩一下沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是鄰居的寶寶在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然隨便摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  人類中的雄性居然比我想像的還要下流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…純  櫻田純
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…倒是  你到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人偶不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫真紅  薔薇少女的第五人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇少女…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這裡還真是髒亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方不適合我居住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很不情願  不過也只好住下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的發條被你轉動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才應該是那麼回答荷裡耶的問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷裡耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被轉動？  難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  這是新的詐騙手法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做得這麼逼真  一定是用遙控器遙控的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我已經受夠你的無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…難道是被詛咒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我瞧不起那些詛咒商品嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我想看看那個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你想看？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我抱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱的方式不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  今後就給我這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後？什麼跟什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夠不到  拿過來給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人類  擁有的人偶還挺不錯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是詛咒用的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來完全不像是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸起來很柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話也像平常人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連長相都像真人  怎麼看都是個女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  連喝杯茶的時間都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  人類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾的  你現在要死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想死  你就要向我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這也太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我死是無所謂  如果你以為能威脅我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  我…我要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了吧  不過是切到衣服罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊！快來救我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是來殺你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類  我再問你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要發誓？還是不發誓？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓  我願意發誓  快點救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請親吻這朵薔薇為證
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好孩子  純
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經成為了我的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒介？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  不好意思  請你們醒來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡作劇是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得救了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的人偶們的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶會選擇自己的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會這樣拚死奮戰  都是為了想保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這代表你不是個壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事…突然有點頭暈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微使點力氣  就累成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個沒用的僕從啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經發誓要保護我真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以成了我的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只薔薇戒指就是證明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著這只戒指的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是通過這只戒指  持續傳給我力量的中介者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所謂的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像剛才那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這件事我可不答應哦  我才不要這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要拿下來的話  你的肉會被扯下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子說你的心破了一個大洞  它很擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞？是在說它自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去泡紅茶給我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅茶  紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  純  你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我本來寫的是JUN(純)  怎麼寫成了JUM…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西  不管你準備多少  都是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你畢竟也升上二年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也說過  升上國二之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有學弟妹  會很好玩的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事根本不用管  就像他們那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽只是因為工作  去了國外而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我不接受任何人的命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不去上學！絕對不去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動！絕對不要動哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡紅茶端進來  馬上泡  聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  一下子叫我不要管他  一下子又叫我泡紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去那裡幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我等太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  你剛才用那種態度  對待淑女實在太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  這跟你這個人偶無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是連講話的態度都不懂的僕從呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒搞清楚自己的立場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙真的很囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好吧  我就讓你見識人類的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的眼睛  眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  我端紅茶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　　　　Orange Pekoe\N{\r}來  這是橙黃白毫茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的話  姐姐跟你一起喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去  這樣可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的杯子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她泡的紅茶向來很難喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  溫度太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶葉也沒有全泡開  香氣都跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這實在談不上是紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種非常溫柔的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  她很疼愛你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想去體會  是不會瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是這壺紅茶的甜美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是這些孩子們的體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  純
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…好不好喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很煩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前…稍微好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好孩子  純
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才是值得琢磨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我選了你當我的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  我才不是你的僕從…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  那個女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細瞧瞧  原來是個人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！說話了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫紀  櫻田紀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這個人偶做得真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道  這就是西洋的充氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  思春期的男生好像都會買這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在書裡看過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你說不是了  快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…  純  不要這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是為什麼  像你這樣的人偶會跑來我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話應該是我說才對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會碰上你這種人做媒介…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  比起這個  先去給我泡茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  兩人份
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為有客人要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:23:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  該不會又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這只薔薇戒指發誓吧
